        <item>
            <title>Nikon Z50II 登場，EXPEED 7 影像處理引擎  + 1 秒「釋放前拍攝」</title>
            <link>https://unwire.hk/2024/11/08/nikon-z50ii/dc/?utm_source=rss&#038;utm_medium=rss&#038;utm_campaign=nikon-z50ii</link>
            <comments>https://unwire.hk/2024/11/08/nikon-z50ii/dc/#respond</comments>
            <dc:creator>
                <![CDATA[Oscar]]>
            </dc:creator>
            <pubDate>Fri, 08 Nov 2024 15:00:11 +0000</pubDate>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[數碼相機]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[EXPEED 7]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[nikon]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[Nikon Z50II]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[Nikon Z9]]>
            </category>
            <guid isPermaLink="false">https://unwire.hk/?p=1273985</guid>
            <description>
                <![CDATA[<p>Nikon 最新推出 Z50II，別因為它機仔細細，使用 APS-C （DX）格式而小看它，其採用與旗艦型號 Z9 相同的 EXPEED 7 影像處理引擎，並加入了不少方便創作的功能，例如增強了對焦準確度和追焦能力量，同時加入全新「Picture Control」按鍵，方便用家快速轉換不同顏色設定。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1273991" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/z50ii_40_2_front34l-687x580.jpg" alt="" width="687" height="580" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/z50ii_40_2_front34l-687x580.jpg 687w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/z50ii_40_2_front34l-1066x900.jpg 1066w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/z50ii_40_2_front34l-scaled.jpg 1067w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 687px" /></p><p>Nikon Z50II 創新增設「成像配方」（Imaging Recipe）功能，提供色彩、亮度、對比度等多重個人化選擇，讓用戶輕鬆切換風格。此外，相機設有全新 Picture Control 按鍵，用戶可即時啟用多種預設色彩設定，無論使用自動模式或手動模式，均可簡單變換濾鏡效果，拍攝更具靈活性。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1273990" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/z50ii_01_jn_1889_z_d-694x463.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="463" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/z50ii_01_jn_1889_z_d-694x463.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/z50ii_01_jn_1889_z_d-scaled.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲成像配方 – Nights like this © Dondre Green</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1273989" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/z50ii_01_dg_5131_z_d-694x463.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="463" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/z50ii_01_dg_5131_z_d-694x463.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/z50ii_01_dg_5131_z_d-scaled.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲成像配方 – 成像配方 – Summertime Cool © Julie Nimke</p><p>Z50II 採用與旗艦型號 Z9 相同的 EXPEED 7 影像處理引擎，支援 Z9 所設的「9 種主體偵測模式」，能自動識別並聚焦動態主體，自動設定 AF 模式，拍攝時即使目標動作多變，也能保持精準對焦。此引擎搭配深度學習技術，能即時分析場景，並自動調整曝光、快門速度和感光度等拍攝設定，用家只需按下快門，便能輕鬆獲得優質影像。配備「釋放前拍攝」功能，更可在完全按下快門釋放按鍵前拍攝影像，緩衝時間長達一秒，不怕錯失重要畫面。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1273993" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/20241108161553-694x464.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="464" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/20241108161553-694x464.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/20241108161553.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p>Z50II 進一步提升影片拍攝性能，具備 5.6K 超取樣功能，可創作高解析度 4K UHD 影片，並支援 N-Log 格式，賦予影片更豐富的色調層次。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1273987" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/z50ii_04_jn_2732_z_d-694x463.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="463" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/z50ii_04_jn_2732_z_d-694x463.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/z50ii_04_jn_2732_z_d-scaled.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1273988" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/z50ii_00_dg_0877_ps-694x463.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="463" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/z50ii_00_dg_0877_ps-694x463.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/z50ii_00_dg_0877_ps-scaled.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p>此外，Z50II 加入影片自拍功能，用家在按下錄影鍵後，能設定 2 秒或 10 秒延遲開始錄影，便於後期編輯處理。Z50II 亦是 Nikon 首部加入產品評價模式的 Z 系相機，相機將會對焦前景物件。除此之外更支援 USB 串流傳輸，只需將相機連接至電腦或手機，即可在網上會議或直播中使用高畫質影像。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1273994" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/20241108161759-694x465.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="465" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/20241108161759-694x465.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/20241108161759.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲可使用 USB 串流直播</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1273995" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/20241108161942-694x465.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="465" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/20241108161942-694x465.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/20241108161942.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲「產品評價模式」下相機將會對焦前景物件</p><p>Z50II 配備亮度達 1000 cd/m² 的電子觀景器，比 Z50 提升近一倍，無論在戶外或室內，用戶都能輕鬆觀察構圖及影像細節，減輕眼部疲勞。通過高亮度 EVF，拍攝時能更專注於主體，輕鬆掌控影像效果，提升拍攝樂趣。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1273996" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/20241108162128-694x463.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="463" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/20241108162128-694x463.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/20241108162128.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p>Z50II 同步推出的 MC-DC3 遙控線，適合夜間拍攝及長時間曝光情境，有效減少相機震動，保持穩定成像。用家可遠距釋放快門，連續拍攝或進行長曝，適合拍攝星空或靜態場景。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1273997" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/27241mcdc3remoteh7az-682x580.png" alt="" width="682" height="580" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/27241mcdc3remoteh7az-682x580.png 682w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/27241mcdc3remoteh7az.png 700w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 682px" /></p><p>The post <a href="https://unwire.hk/2024/11/08/nikon-z50ii/dc/">Nikon Z50II 登場，EXPEED 7 影像處理引擎  + 1 秒「釋放前拍攝」</a> appeared first on <a href="https://unwire.hk">UNWIRE.HK</a>.</p>
]]>
            </description>
